summary: This mod fills the treasure room in the Thives Guild HQ.
descriptionHtml:
[u]Description:[/u]

This mod fills the treasure room in the Thives Guild HQ. (see pictures) Even if you already played the TG questline.
There is a key in the ragged floaggon cistern that opens the door, but first you have to find it.
Small hint: Mercer

[u]Credits:[/u]

I used some objects from the great "[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/16525/?]Modder's Resource Pack[/url]" by [b]Oaristys and Tony67
[/b]
author: skoomaface
